dataIdInfo.idAbs: This point data layer represents addresses for Pierce County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Pierce_Addresses_2017.[Address locations in Pierce County. Points for the most part are located on building/structures. ]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [Address points - location of addresses in Pierce County. Used for e911 and other mapping products.]
